17
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:30,910
Siapa mencekik leher awak?

18
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,360
Saya tak kenal dia.

19
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:34,260
Cuba tengok, orang inikah?

20
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,410
Ya, dia orangnya.

21
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:39,680
Awak pasti?

22
