30
00:03:56,070 --> 00:03:56,660
Ya.

31
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:06,090
Pintu ini asalnya ada dua ibu kunci?

32
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:07,130
Tak.

33
00:04:07,370 --> 00:04:09,510
Sejak bila ada satu lagi ibu kunci?

34
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,570
Nanti,

35
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,810
kita mula menyiasat ibu kunci dulu.

36
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:14,980
Saya akan beritahu mereka.

37
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,550
Awak dengar apa-apa

38
00:04:28,550 --> 00:04:29,990
