39
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:30,980
Tak.

40
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:32,700
Tiada bunyi langsung.

41
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:35,020
Lampu di rumah itu pun tak pernah dinyalakan.

42
00:04:35,350 --> 00:04:37,540
Semua penghuni di lorong ini

43
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:40,220
