44
00:04:40,490 --> 00:04:41,240
Semua orang tahu.

45
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:45,030
Pernahkah sesiapa datang selepas itu?

46
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,100
Tiada.

47
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:48,310
Jika seseorang datang, saya pasti nampaknya.

48
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,960
Pemilik No. 1A dah meninggal dunia.

49
00:04:53,230 --> 00:04:54,220
Anak-anaknya berkata

50
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,909
