138
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,570
Ada lagi penemuan lain?

139
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,539
Sisa pencuci

140
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:39,390
berkepekatan tinggi

141
00:08:39,419 --> 00:08:40,950
dikesan di seluruh rumah.

142
00:08:40,970 --> 00:08:41,950
Ini bermaksud seseorang

143
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,220
