175
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:36,660
Han Qing.

176
00:09:37,060 --> 00:09:38,490
Saya sebaliknya nak percaya itulah dia.

177
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:40,470
Tahukah sebabnya?

178
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:42,330
Sebab saya harap dia masih hidup.

179
00:09:42,610 --> 00:09:43,810
Saya harap dia boleh beritahu saya bersemuka

